        <div class="order-1 sm:order-2 flex flex-col lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8 ">

            <h1 class="text-3xl  text-[#1c5a88] font-bold mb-3 ">Subsidy</h1>
            <p class="font-medium">
                Haryana offers a range of subsidies and incentives to attract and support investors through its "Invest Haryana" initiative. 
            <br />
                <br />
                These incentives are designed to make Haryana an attractive destination for investment by reducing the cost of doing business and enhancing profitability for enterprises.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Image -->
        <div class=" order-3  lg:w-1/2">
            <div class="relative">
                <img src="assets/images/single-person.jpg" alt="Team Working" class="rounded-xl ">
                <!-- Decorative Element -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 bg-[#991c20] w-20 h-20 rounded-bl-full"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
